killed President
John F. Kennedy.

01:30.824 --> 01:33.961 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP (R), Presidential
Candidate:
His father with was Lee Harvey
Oswald prior

01:34.061 --> 01:39.333 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
