Indiana.

02:49.770 --> 02:52.439 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEN. BERNIE SANDERS (VT-I),
Presidential Candidate:
These trade agreements, whether
it's NAFTA

02:52.539 --> 02:57.444 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
