20:28.160 --> 20:33.532 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The New York Times' Declan Walsh
recently
returned from Damascus and
Syria's largest

20:33.632 --> 20:37.503 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
